      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, dependable condition and has been well-maintained over the years. The exterior is very presentable, though it does show some light surface scratches and a few small stone chips consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster and some light scuffing on the plastic trim. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
